<subSubSection pageId="143" pageNumber="714" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="143.[2092,2678,1693,2115]" pageId="143" pageNumber="714">
Formerly considered a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Thunberg" baseAuthorityYear="1789" class="Mammalia" family="Bovidae" genus="Philantomba" kingdom="Animalia" order="Artiodactyla" pageId="143" pageNumber="714" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="monticola">P monticola</taxonomicName>
. Split by some authors into subspecies based on the mountain ranges inhabited, but treated as monotypic here. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[2093,2603,1964,1997]" pageId="143" pageNumber="714" type="distribution">
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6512827" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6512827" box="[2093,2603,1964,1997]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6512827/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="143" pageNumber="714" targetBox="[1475,2069,1697,2114]" targetPageId="143">
<paragraph blockId="143.[2092,2678,1693,2115]" box="[2093,2603,1964,1997]" pageId="143" pageNumber="714">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[2093,2268,1964,1997]" pageId="143" pageNumber="714">Distribution.</emphasis>
